Narrator

On entering the building, we were met by a parliamentary guide who briefed us about the procedures. After a strict security screening, the staff ushered us to the third floor.

Narrator

I, Deivid Wisci and the rest of the Sordish delegation to the Alliance of Nations arrived in Kyrute. The local police escorted us to the Alliance's headquarters in downtown Konstantium, immediately recognizable by its gleaming dome.

Patricio Alvarez

"Mr. President, it is my pleasure to return to this podium."

Patricio Alvarez

"...Today, the need to come together as the leaders of the free world is more important than ever."

Patricio Alvarez

"We hereby call for the immediate dismantling and withdrawal of all missiles and other offensive weapons from Heljiland."

Patricio Alvarez

"We hereby call for the immediate withdrawal of all naval vessels with any offensive capability from international waters."

Player_Italic

I did not reply and kept listening to Alvarez.

Narrator

Deivid leaned in and spoke in a low voice.

Player

"Look at that guy... He's an embarrassment."

Narrator

The president of the assembly slammed his gavel down and called for restraint.

Narrator

Deivid looked concerned.

Player

"Do you think that's true?"

Patricio Alvarez

"Let us also not forget about the recent events that transpired in an another state with socialist teachings. A state that wages war against its own innocent citizens. Wehlen."

Player

"That's a bunch of horseshit. Wehlen is not even socialist."

Patricio Alvarez

"Lespia was affected not only by the large wave of refugees coming from Wehlen, but by the subsequent government seizure of all of our companies that were active in the country."

Narrator

Deivid held my shoulder.

Narrator

Player

"That's an empty argument. It doesn't justify what Wehlen did."

"Honorable chairman and fellow delegates to the Alliance of Nations."

Leon Malenyev

"Here we are again at the most esteemed meeting of state representatives in the world."

"We will not be silent anymore against these lies! When was this peace you talk about? Where was this cooperation between our countries? Have you ever accepted our invitation to talk about de-nuclearization?"
